content: Total revenue was $64.7 million, up 30% year-over-year, driven primarily by continued strong sales of our Cloud solutions, as well as by solid growth in professional services revenue. SaaS and support revenue was $47 million up 36% year-over-year, reflecting both new sales to new clients and upsales and cross-sales to existing clients of Intapp purpose-built cloud solutions.
